---
title: Creamy Chicken Curry with Green Beans and Fluffy Rice
description: We believe that sharing is caring, which is why it’s no secret what makes our creamy chicken curry so delicious. The Sri Lankan style curry blend in this dish is a mix of some classic Sri Lankan spices and herbs like cardamom, fenugreek seeds and cayenne. You’ll rarely find this blend anywhere else and it really portrays the true taste of Sri Lanka.
